@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vadlvx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 1.00
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin((v0 + 0.92 / v2 + 0.54)))
    v0 = 0.74
    tmp = v1
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.cos(v2))
    v0 = ((v2 / wp.sin(v2 + 0.26)) + wp.abs((v0 + 0.36 - v1 + 0.83)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.36)) * ((v1 + 0.44 + v0 + 0.54) / 0.46))
    tmp = (1.00 / tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
